tion in case\nof antiferromagnetic coupling and may be one of the reasons of the observed\nlower magnetic ordering temperature of the doped systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Nov 2021 22:48:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Jan 2022 05:21:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2022 22:52:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-26"}
