, and that models of the\ndynamics of entanglements might be improved upon by considering a tensorial\nmeasurement of entanglements that can be coupled to orientation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Nov 2021 01:33:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Feb 2022 20:59:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
