ly impacts single-epoch black hole mass estimates by $\\sim0.1$ dex on\naverage and possibly up to $\\sim0.3-0.5$ dex individually.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Nov 2021 04:23:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Dec 2021 03:38:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
