t templates at the\nlower ML component-level are also developed based on the RAM. Finally, to\nevaluate and demonstrate our methods, we not only conduct experiments on\nsynthetic/benchmark datasets but also scope our methods with case studies on\nsimulated Autonomous Underwater Vehicles and physical Unmanned Ground Vehicles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Nov 2021 14:39:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2022 15:01:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-16"}
